Description: Blast Off Comedy is making the city of love the city of laughs! All of our comedy shows are 100% in English and every show features a different line-up so each show is unique!! The All Stars showcase features the very best from the Paris comedy scene as well as comics touring in Europe! Our past guests have been featured on Comedy Central, Netflix, and Amazon including Mark Normand, Jeff Ross, Sam Tallent, Usama Siddiquee, and Elena Gabrielle. So you never know who's going to pop-in! Why does the ticket cost 1,27‚Ç¨? This small fee reserves your spot at the show and helps us manage the capacity at the venue as seating is limited. And in fact, we don't keep any of this money and it all goes to Eventbrite. The business model of our show is that it is crowd funded üôÇ That means you can enter the show with a very small reservation fee + the purchase of a drink (for the bar) and that you pay what you can after the show to support the artists. This allows people who can't afford to come to a normal ticketed show to experience live comedy at a reasonable price! For those who can afford it, we like to suggest 12‚Ç¨ per person and 7‚Ç¨ for students. Thank you for supporting live comedy!
Title: English Stand Up Comedy - Sundays - Blast Off Comedy All Stars
